cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper is about automatic speech recognition, which is a subfield of natural language processing. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with speech signals and their processing. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a model based on unsupervised learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with developing a more robust ASR system using machine learning techniques. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with improving the performance of a system (ASR) under varying conditions.
